detail.name: Spaceship of Hope
detail.effect: [Activate Main/Battle] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck, then reveal up to 1 card that includes <GT> in its card name and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of its owner's deck in a random order.

detail.name: 希望の宇宙船
detail.effect: 【起動 メイン/戦闘中】自分のデッキの上から5枚を見て、カード名に「GT」を含むカード1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
